{"tid":1779023,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"亞視(偽香港)航空被愛爾蘭公司入稟追約2.7億港元","createTime":"2019-12-11T11:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T12:29:29.000Z","uid":176981,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cee07ff774d0ff57b576063af068d83d1bfe6dce","tid":1779023,"uid":176981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"香港航空剛於上週避過被釘牌的危機，但又再捲入民事訴訟。一間愛爾蘭公司指香港航空未有遵照英國法院於上月的頒令，向該公司支付約2.7億港元。該公司昨(10日)入稟高院，向港航追討欠款和利息。<br />\n<br />\n原告為Alafco Irish Aircraft Leasing Sixteen Limited，被告為香港航空有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指，英國法院於上月22日頒令，被告需於本月6號下午4時前向原告支付3400多萬美元和19萬英鎊，即折合約2.7億元港元。惟被告未有支付該筆款項，原告因此入稟追討。<br />\n<br />\n香港航空回應稱，正與飛機租賃公司積極溝通，以期達成解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA2276/2019<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/408638/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%84%9B%E7%88%BE%E8%98%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E8%BF%BD%E7%B4%842-7%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F408638%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25B4%25842-7%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=bab8c469\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/408638/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%84%9B%E7%88%BE%E8%98%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E8%BF%BD%E7%B4%842-7%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83</a>"},{"pid":"5f2c965941230f936849194ca37b11e630db66ba","tid":1779023,"uid":176981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"亞視永痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a